thread.title: Joshua

author: Joshua
title: Joshua
text:
Clarity- this review is only 4 stars because the product hasn't been planted outside yet and thus I do not know if they are Georgia weather hardy as their zone rating advertises. It's winger time and it can still get cold enough to kill a plant under the stress of replanting/rooting/coming out of being dormant.
Having said that, the products arrived not just timely, but seemingly with an to grow right off the bat. My bananas are growing full leaves inside (under a lamp next to a full sun window) and my quince tree has enough new growth on it 2-3 weeks in that I am trimming leaves and tethering it to keep it straight and growing.
I will definitely, at this time, buy from this place again.
